description:
Descend deep below Fortuna in the latest major Warframe update: The Vallis Undermind! Come to the aid of Nightcap and command a fungal network with the mushroom Warframe, Nokko. Protect the Sprodlings from greedy Corpus clutches and you will be greatly rewarded.

Add new Customizations to your Arsenal with the Wukong Qitian and Lavos Khymia Collections.

Start playing The Vallis Undermind on all platforms today! https://epic.gm/warframepdp
